{"tid":2078240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美將華為、中移動、中鐵建等 20 國企列解放軍控制名單　鋪路制裁或封鎖資產","createTime":"2020-06-25T01:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T03:13:54.000Z","uid":51665,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4be759a79df6252949fc6edf58233242be870d6a","tid":2078240,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T01:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/huawe_5bFTq_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fhuawe_5bFTq_1200x0.png&h=46789678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透社及美國網媒 Axios 均獲得一份美國官方文件，顯示特朗普政府決定將包括華為在內的 20 家中資巨企列為由解放軍支持及控制。意味美國可能對名單內的中資公司實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n除華為之外，名單還包括視頻監控設備製造商海康威視、中國移動、中國電信、中國航空工業集團。網媒 Axios 的報道則指，中國航天科技、中國鐵建、中國廣核集團、中國中車、熊貓電子集團、中科曙光、經營雲計算大數據等業務的浪潮集團、中國航空發動機集團、中國南方工業等公司都榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n名單由美國國防部根據 1999 年的國防授權法彙編，今次是首度曝光。路透社獲國防部消息人士確認，並稱已呈交國會。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道指，特朗普有權制裁名單上的公司，包括封鎖其資產（blocking all property of the listed parties）。美國去年以國防理由，把華為列入貿易黑名單，並向國際盟友游說不要採用華為的 5G 技術。<br />\n<br />\n Axios引述消息指，上榜的都是「尋常嫌疑犯」（usual suspects），部分公司同解放軍有聯繫，但亦會獨立收集情報。一名前官員則說：「如果沒有制裁行動（包括禁止在美國營運），這（公開名單）只不過吠了一聲，不是咬一口。」（&ldquo;It&rsquo;s a bark, not a bite, if sanctions (to include prohibition from doing business in the U.S.) don&rsquo;t follow,&quot; ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%AD%E9%90%B5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%89-20-%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E5%88%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-%E9%8B%AA%E8%B7%AF%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%88%96%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589-20-%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE-%25E9%258B%25AA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2%2F&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=9675e5b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%25AD%2589-20-%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE-%25E9%258B%25AA%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2%2F&h=fdfdd91e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA-%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%AD%E9%90%B5%E5%BB%BA%E7%AD%89-20-%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E5%88%97%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-%E9%8B%AA%E8%B7%AF%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E6%88%96%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508953c2adbae6318470b7e70581cd9edf459b1a","tid":2078240,"uid":1544,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"幾時封埋騰訊 百度 阿里"},{"pid":"57f651166d51c9983dfbfcc3dbbbdc630d7d9243","tid":2078240,"uid":5490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"508953c2adbae6318470b7e70581cd9edf459b1a","tid":2078240,"uid":1544,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"幾時封埋騰訊 百度 阿里"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020